Hurt can be found on the 'American IV' album here, http://thepiratebay.org/tor/3279290/Johnny_Cash_-_American_IV_-_The_Man_Comes_Around_(as_requested)

It should be noted that it was originally a song by the Nine Inch Nails that Cash covered.

This is a nice collection, but there is far more than a few tracks missing, or just a few albums. It's not even close to being complete through 1993 as someone had suggested. Through 1993, Johnny Cash had 83 albums, and that's not including 29 compilation albums.
